# docs/ is intentionally tracked — holds PROJECT_QA.md and any human-authored
# reference docs. (Auto-generated docs would be a separate concern; nothing
# generates into docs/ today.)
# docs/private/ is local-only — drop any purely personal notes there (interview
# rehearsals, salary thoughts, target-company lists, etc.) and they'll never
# leave your machine. Create the directory locally when you need it.
docs/private/
